message.content: Okay, first thing we have to clean up our workspace directory so we have some duplicates. So you see, in the main workspace directory, we have an agent workspace and this agent workspace has a docs directory with architecture and project overview docs. Now, this agent workspace in the top directory is a duplicate because it needs to be inside my Jarvis directory. Inside my Jarvis, we have projects, inside project, we have my Jarvis desktop and in there, we have an agent workspace. So let's start by just deleting this agent workspace in the top workspace directory. Just like confirm this to me before, show me that you understand exactly which directory I'm talking about before you delete it.
